          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "With all the challenges of 2020, there doesn’t seem to be a shortage of people who want to take advantage of others. From ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
